<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>OTP Verification</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f2f2f2;
      }
      
      .container {
        max-width: 500px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 5px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      
      h1 {
        color: #0055a5;
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      
      p {
        color: #333333;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      
      .otp-container {
        background-color: #e6f2ff;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      
      .otp {
        color: #0055a5;
        font-size: 36px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>OTP Verification</h1>
      <p>Please use the following one-time password (OTP) to verify your identity:</p>
      <div class="otp-container">
        <span class="otp"><%= otp %></span>
      </div>
      <p>This OTP is valid for <%= expirationTime %> minutes.</p>
      <p>If you did not request this OTP, please ignore this email.</p>
      <p>Thank you,<br>Optimum ERP</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>